	(text "The relay is switched to the NO \ncontact (without attenuation)\nwhen the attenuated voltage is\nmeasured and calculated to be\nactually less than 3.3 volts \nto increase the resolution.\n\nThe jumpers are used to select\nthe desired attenuation value\nthus varying the maximum allowable\nvoltage."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 121.158 121.92 0)
